title: Levi Strauss Signature Gold Women's Modern Bootcut Jeans (Also Available in Plus)
description: Same great jeans, brand new name! Signature by Levi Strauss & Co. is now Levi Strauss Signature Gold
Super stretch lasts from day to night; Snug fit doesn't lose shape

Work, play, and face the day with Signature by Levi Strauss & Co.™ Women's Mid-Rise Boot Cut Jeans. Crafted from ultra-comfortable Simply Stretch denim, this trusty denim pair has a modern boot cut and soft, lightweight fabric that smooths and lifts but doesn’t constrict. Signature by Levi Strauss & Co.™ Women's Mid-rise Boot cut Jeans are your go-to, slimming leg denim that effortlessly hug curves and offer excellent flexibility, dynamic comfort, and a perfect fit.
